      <title>0.1.26</title>
      <description><![CDATA[<h3>What's new in 0.1.26</h3><ul><li>The notch widget now stays visible (dimmed) while your watched tools are running but idle, instead of disappearing every time the Mac is briefly allowed to sleep. It only hides when keep-awake is off or nothing is running.</li>
<li>Added launch, quit and hand-off entries to the diagnostics log to make troubleshooting easier.</li></ul>]]></description>
